response.overview: Like a real life ROCKY story, this intense feature documentary tells the story of married professional wrestlers Francisco Ciatso and Stormie Lee. Not only is the audience introduced to a world of wrestling that isn't the glitz and glamour of WWE, but the camera becomes intimate with the husband and wife wrestlers as they deal with money and relationship issues.
response.tagline: Like a real life ROCKY story, this intense documentary tells the story of a married couple of professional wrestlers.
response.title: Journeyman
